<p style="text-align: justify;">Blake started her acting career at the age of 10 as Trixie, the Tooth Fairy in the musical movie <strong>Sandman </strong>(1998), directed by her father. Blake was about to finish high school when she landed one of the major roles of her career as Bridget in <strong>The Sisterhood of Travelling Pants</strong> (2005). She then played a lead role in the movie <strong>Elvis and Anabella</strong> for which she was widely praised, and it was considered as her breakthrough role. Later, from 2007 to-2012, she acted on The CWâ€™s beloved teen drama series, <strong>Gossip Girl, </strong>as Serena Van der Woodsen and gained immense popularity from it.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Subsequently, in the following years, she acted in many movies such as <strong>The Sisterhood of Travelling Pants 2</strong> (2008), <strong>New York I love you</strong> (2009), <strong>The Private Lives of Pippa Lee</strong> (2009), Â <strong>The town</strong> (2010)<strong>, Green Lantern</strong> (2011), <strong>Savages</strong> (2012), <strong>The age of Adaline</strong> (2015) and <strong>The Shallows</strong> (2016). Her acting skills were appreciated in all of her movies. Moreover, she was also filmed in the music video forÂ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Lonely_Island">The Lonely Island</a>'s "<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I_Just_Had_Sex">IÂ Just Had Sex</a>".</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Other interests</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Blake is also an aspiring cook and an interior decorator. She was featured baking a cake in an episode of popular talk show <strong>The Martha Steward Show</strong> in 2008. Also, in 2010, she spent some time as a pastry chef in renowned restaurant <strong>Per Se</strong> in New York. Furthermore, she has also filmed a cooking segment for <strong>Vogueâ€™s</strong> <a href="http://www.wikiceleb.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">magazine</a>. She is expected to launch Preserve, a digital and e-commerce websites with handmade unique items.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Personal life</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Lively is wife to actor Ryan Reynolds whom she met while filming Green Lantern in 2010 and got married in September 2012. At present, they live with their two beautiful daughters named James and Ines in Bedford, New York.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Achievements</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Blakeâ€™s role in Gossip Girl bagged two teen-choice awards for <em>choice TV actress</em> <em>drama</em> in 2008 and 2011. Furthermore, she has won the Best Ensemble award from Washington D.C.Â  Area Film Critics Association in 2010 for her movie <em>The Towns</em>. Blake was also featured in the annualÂ <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_Magazine"><em>TIME</em>Â magazine</a>Â as one of the 100 most influential people in 2011. On top of that,Â <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AskMen.com">AskMen.com</a>Â entitled her the most desirable woman of 2011, and in the following year, Peopleâ€™s magazine named her one of the 2012's Most Beautiful at Every Age. Moreover, she has won Peopleâ€™s choice awards for favorite dramatic movie actress for her movie <em>The Shallows</em> in 2017.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Â </strong><strong>Future Plans</strong></p>
